title: Fall Graduate Expo to Highlight Scholarship Opportunities (Texas A&M University - Commerce)
text: ( Source : Texas A&M University - Commerce ) On Tuesday, November 3 from 4:30 to 7 p.m., Texas A&M University-Commerce will host a Grad Expo at Eastfield College located at 3737 Motley Drive , Mesquite, Texas 75150. 'A& M-Commerce
